@QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Register a new user
POST {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### Login
POST {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Create a quotation (requires JWT)
POST {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/quotes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quoteNumber": "Q-1001",
  "customerId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "amount": 1250.00,
  "description": "Security camera installation",
  "quoteDate": "2026-06-11T00:00:00Z"
}

### Get all quotations
GET {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/quotes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get quotation by ID
GET {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/quotes/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get dashboard metrics
GET {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### WhatsApp webhook verification (GET)
GET {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/webhooks/whatsapp?hub_mode=subscribe&hub_verify_token=your_verify_token&hub_challenge=123456

### WhatsApp webhook for messages (POST)
POST {{QuoteFlowAI_HostAddress}}/api/webhooks/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "object": "whatsapp_business_account",
  "entry": []
}